      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "颜色方案很好，D用#e1f5fe浅蓝，E用#f3e5f5浅紫，F用#e8f5e8浅绿。F节点是runtime解释器，标签写\"Интерпретация в runtime\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "F",
        "style D",
        "style E",
        "style F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三个样式已应用。F节点通过\"Доступ к B-деревьям\"连接到G，G是最终结果返回。整个流程闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
